.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-12::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, indie
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil
1. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the architect##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | writing   | rock-climbing |
| Job           | architect | dressmaker    |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | indie         |
| Flower         | iris   | daffodil |

