.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-13::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, dutch
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, july
1. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the fan of ambient##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | juice   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | dubstep |
| Nationality   | canadian | dutch   |
| Birthday           | july  | august    |

