.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-18::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, pepper
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, metal
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, rugby
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the fan of jazz is the person eating apricot##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |
| Food          | apricot    | pepper |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | metal  |
| Sport         | rowing     | rugby  |
| Cigar     | havana | swisher |

