The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, sudoku
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the doctor is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Hobby         | writing          | sudoku     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 